One of the first photos taken from one of the two helicopters that first reached the survivors.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Alive-andes-4.jpg" class="image" title="Parrado and his friends after the rescue."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Alive-andes-4.jpg/300px-Alive-andes-4.jpg" width="300" height="251" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
